{"tid":1301990,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"[廣東省] 大灣區警察/律師/法院","createTime":"2019-07-09T19:46:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-10T21:45:20.000Z","uid":260806,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"c73a9b6a36ad602cfc336bc8a2e08e745d92a6fb","tid":1301990,"uid":260806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T19:46:24.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.gd.gov.cn/gdywdt/gdyw/content/post_2530521.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.gd.gov.cn%2Fgdywdt%2Fgdyw%2Fcontent%2Fpost_2530521.html&d=aELkmJ%2FgRhSQUMA2B8lhBNMQoCHxbgs64DeXVNsql00%3D&h=19626e7b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.gd.gov.cn/gdywdt/gdyw/content/post_2530521.html</a><br />\n广东印发推进粤港澳大湾区建设三年行动计划（2018-2020年）<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">71.深化社会治理合作。支持大湾区内地九市的区（县）与香港、澳门片区、堂区建立结对交流机制。在大湾区内地港澳居民比较集中的城乡社区，拓展社会综合服务功能。建立大湾区<span style=\"color: red;\">社会治安治理联动机制</span>，加强粤港澳警务合作交流。建立<span style=\"color: red;\">粤港澳突发事件应急处置联动机制</span>和应急协调平台。<br />\n<br />\n74.推进营商环境法治化建设。探索开展营商环境地方立法工作。加强粤港澳司法交流与协作，建设<span style=\"color: red;\">国际法律及争议解决服务中心</span>，推动建立多元化纠纷解决机制。推动成立服务&ldquo;一带一路&rdquo;建设的法律类社会组织，加快推进&ldquo;一带一路&rdquo;法治地图建设。支持建立<span style=\"color: red;\">粤港澳律师联合会</span>。推动建设<span style=\"color: red;\">大湾区国际仲裁中心</span>。</span><br />\n<br />\n三大重點：<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">香港警察將會歸屬大灣區聯動機制管理。<br />\n香港律師會被合併。<br />\n香港法院會被取代。</span>"},{"pid":"469608f48eeb01546bd61a3222f7a92a698beb80","tid":1301990,"uid":71085,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T20:26:35.000Z","msg":"Bookmarked聽朝推"},{"pid":"ad53432c0a11efc9b04aa6397cf14e5b7e39b333","tid":1301990,"uid":233325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T20:31:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2c3e249e64cf9393ba07c301948dbd90462f0ea","tid":1301990,"uid":233325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T20:33:40.000Z","msg":"其實個甚麼社會信用評分都係係大灣區發展綱要下<br />\n<br />\n拒絕香港融入大灣區<br />\n香港只係一個區<br />\n叫香港特別行政區<br />\n<br />\n#我唔要入大灣區"},{"pid":"1a07c87b3cb81b0c6dd878cd448820b2a057893c","tid":1301990,"uid":58841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T20:39:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/LAe5iPJ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLAe5iPJ.png&h=895175c2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"335323c0fdbeedc100be6cb57a04fc2944d64932","tid":1301990,"uid":97240,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T20:39:10.000Z","msg":"迫人起革命<br />\n<br />\n反正都死,為香港死仲光榮"},{"pid":"8254bb21f1e42536289627189c89194cf2615168","tid":1301990,"uid":177338,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T20:40:22.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"45420a2c91024431673cb9866a8f979de9529987","tid":1301990,"uid":71085,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T07:10:54.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"181eb70cf8a7d7b661b89d84939b424698b74cad","tid":1301990,"uid":261316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T07:13:58.000Z","msg":"我冇野講"},{"pid":"c4ff31eb8b70a3f6a1c6f0ada178db64853cdabe","tid":1301990,"uid":14305,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T07:20:35.000Z","msg":"唔識睇 唔想睇 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iw26Roa.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fiw26Roa.gif&h=c3d7aec4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a236a1025a9079d86a57ecb94b7bbbf8a36f2953","tid":1301990,"uid":71085,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T07:22:37.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0354d8f000e52fc694bd18c0cf8ee08f16906991","tid":1301990,"uid":258192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T07:29:22.000Z","msg